2. Write a function to store "G_Str_SteeringAngle_sint" to "G_Msg_SteeringInformation_Byte" as shown below.
signed int G_Str_SteeringAngle_sint = -60;
unsigned char G_Msg_SteeringInformation_Byte[3u];"

ALGRORITHM
1)Instalize the unsigned character and variable and array size of 3.
2)Read the inputs.
3)Check the bits in SteeringAngle .
4)In SteeringAngle_sint  10,11 bits are assign for array of 0 
5)In SteeringAngle_sint  2 to 9 bits are assign for array of 1
6)In SteeringAngle_sint 0,1 bits are assign for array of 2
7)For loop or checking the bits.
8)check the result.
